<subSubSection pageId="35" pageNumber="34" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="35.[192,1440,1570,1658]" pageId="35" pageNumber="34">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[192,303,1570,1594]" pageId="35" pageNumber="34">Remark</emphasis>
. The geographic distribution provided by 
<bibRefCitation author="Lindroth, C. H." box="[812,1004,1570,1594]" pageId="35" pageNumber="34" pagination="161 - 198" refId="ref33972" refString="Lindroth, C. H. 1976. Genus Bembidion Latreille (Coleoptera: Carabidae) in New Zealand: a revision. New Zealand Journal of Zoology 3: 161 - 198." type="journal article" year="1976">Lindroth (1976)</bibRefCitation>
for this species included records for 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Broun" authorityYear="1886" box="[192,478,1602,1626]" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="35" pageNumber="34" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nesophilum">
<emphasis box="[192,478,1602,1626]" italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="34">Bembidion nesophilum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
which is resurrected from synonymy in the current revision. 
<taxonomicName authorityName=": Lindroth" authorityYear="1976" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Bembidion" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="35" pageNumber="34" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="callipeplum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="35" pageNumber="34">Bembidion callipeplum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is now known from numerous localities, mostly in southern areas of the North Island.
</paragraph>
